H.K. SFC Reprimands, Fines Citigroup Global Markets Asia

-- B y   B i l l y   C h a n
-- 
2011-10-03T09:33:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/h-k-sfc-reprimands-fines-citigroup-global-markets-asia.html
Hong Kong ’s Securities and Futures
Commission reprimanded and fined Citigroup Global Markets Asia
Ltd. HK$6 million, it said in a statement today.  Citi Asia has “also agreed to offer to pay compensation to
customers affected by a fraudulent scheme operated by a former
licensed representative in the amount of any principal lost by
such customers,” the statement said.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Billy Chan in Hong Kong at 
 bchan101@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
